What is dbt?

dbt is a data tool

dbt is a transformation tool

CLOUD DW -> SNOWFLAKE, REDSHIFT BIGQUERY 

ETL -> EXTRACT TRANSFORM AND LOAD(DW) -> BI AI ML

ELT -> EXTRACT LOAD AND TRANSFORM INTO A DW -> BI AI ML

OBS: ITS NOT A ETL OR ELT TOOL, ITS JUST TO TRANSFORM DATA AFTER OR BEFORE LOADED TO A DW

RAW DATA -> DBT -> TRANSFORMED DATA

